Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:38.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}君がそばにいてくれるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:42.27,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}羽ばたく誓いの空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:45.39,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}この手伸ばすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:49.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}儚い夢を 君の涙を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}守る輝きになりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:22:58.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}残酷に染められた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:01.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}その瞳を解き放て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:04.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}信じてる
